      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="font-semibold">Tailored technology:</strong> We have deep experience with platforms like CKAN, our own <a href="https://data.gift" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-500">data.gift</a>, and custom solutions — so you always get the right fit.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

{{! Four Levels of Data Sharing Section }}
<section class="container mb-16">
  <h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-zinc-900">
    Four ways we help you share your data
  </h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <ServiceCard
      @illustration="/assets/vector/level-0.svg"
      @title="Level 0: Entry-level sharing"
      @text="Share your data with minimal effort. We connect your data to major European portals (such as data.europa.eu) through a simple setup. No maintenance or technical hassle for you. Get instant visibility while we handle the background details."
      @benefits={{array "Ideal for first-time publishers" "No portal upkeep" "Maximum reach with minimal resources"}}
    />

    <ServiceCard
      @illustration="/assets/vector/level-1.svg"
      @title="Level 1: Catalog portals"
      @text="Show off your datasets without moving them or making extra copies. We make it easy to create a clean, searchable overview of everything you offer, while your actual data stays where it is."
      @benefits={{array "Save time and storage" "Avoid messy sync problems" "Easy data discovery"}}
    />

    <ServiceCard
      @illustration="/assets/vector/level-2.svg"
      @title="Level 2: Powerful data portals"
      @text="Manage, host, and deliver your datasets with one modern platform built just for you. You get easy uploads, strong user controls, ready-made APIs, and smart automation."
      @benefits={{array "Full control over data sharing" "Professional features" "Built for compliance and growth"}}
    />

    <ServiceCard
      @illustration="/assets/vector/level-3.svg"
      @title="Level 3: Connected knowledge platforms"
      @text="Turn your data into a living network. Every file and datapoint gets its own web address and links to related information, making everything easier to find and use. Based on our reliable data.gift platform."
      @benefits={{array "Future-ready and scalable" "Innovation-focused" "Integrated digital ecosystems"}}
    />
  </div>
</section>

